text: TCG Birinci İnönü ("First Inonu") sometimes written as I. İnönü, is the name of several Turkish submarines, named in commemoration of the Turkish victory at the First Battle of İnönü in January 1921 It can refer to: * , built at Fijenoord, acquired 1928, decommissioned 1948 * , ex -USS Brill (S-330), an un-modified Balao-class submarine acquired 1948, decommissioned 1972 * , ex USS Threadfin (S-410), a Balao-class GUPPY IIA submarine acquired 1972, decommissioned 1998 * , a Gür class submarine built in 2007 ==See also== * TCG Ikinci İnönü Category:Turkish Navy ship names
title: TCG Birinci İnönü
